text.tspan: May there be nothing else taking Your place.
Everything other than You is a waste.
Lord, make me willing to pay any price
To gain the oil, to be filled up with Christ.
Lord, may I open and gain You each day
In such a steady and unfailing way.
On Your name I would call,
Fill all my vision, remain in my view.
As I’m beholding my life reflects You.
